| Spending analytics/reports | | рҹ”® |
| Family/shared plans | | рҹ”® |
| Mobile app (PWA or native) | | рҹ”® |
| Bill splitting | | рҹ”® |
| Export data (CSV/PDF) | | рҹ”® |

### 1.4 Success Metrics & Retention Hooks

| Metric | Target (30 days) |
|--------|-------------------|
| Sign-ups | 500 |
| D7 retention | 40% |
| Items added per user | вүҘ 3 |
| Free вҶ’ Paid conversion | 5вҖ“8% |
| Monthly churn (paid) | < 10% |

**Retention hooks:**
- **Calendar as habit loop** вҖ” users return monthly to mark payments
- **"Monthly total" guilt/awareness** вҖ” shows RM total, motivates tracking
- **Missed payment indicator** вҖ” red badges create urgency to return
- **Streak counter** (later) вҖ” "5 months of on-time payments!"

