## 2. Data Entry Fields

### 2.1 Subscription Item

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Validation | Example |
|-------|------|----------|---------|------------|---------|
| `name` | string | вң… Must-have | вҖ” | 1вҖ“100 chars | "Netflix" |
| `amount` | decimal | вң… Must-have | вҖ” | > 0, max 99999.99 | 54.90 |
| `currency` | string | вң… Must-have | `MYR` | ISO 4217 | "MYR" |
| `billing_cycle` | enum | вң… Must-have | `monthly` | weekly / monthly / yearly | "monthly" |
| `billing_day` | int | вң… Must-have | 1 | 1вҖ“31 (clamped to month length) | 15 |
| `start_date` | date | вң… Must-have | today | valid date | "2025-01-15" |
| `category` | enum | Optional | `other` | predefined list | "entertainment" |
| `notes` | string | Optional | вҖ” | max 500 chars | "Family plan, shared" |
| `color` | string | Optional | auto-assigned | hex color | "#FF6B6B" |
| `is_active` | boolean | вң… Must-have | `true` | вҖ” | true |

### 2.2 BNPL / Installment Item

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Validation | Example |
|-------|------|----------|---------|------------|---------|
| `name` | string | вң… Must-have | вҖ” | 1вҖ“100 chars | "iPhone 16 Atome" |
| `installment_amount` | decimal | вң… Must-have | вҖ” | > 0, max 99999.99 | 150.00 |
| `total_installments` | int | вң… Must-have | вҖ” | 1вҖ“120 | 6 |
| `currency` | string | вң… Must-have | `MYR` | ISO 4217 | "MYR" |
| `billing_cycle` | enum | вң… Must-have | `monthly` | weekly / biweekly / monthly | "monthly" |
| `billing_day` | int | вң… Must-have | 1 | 1вҖ“31 | 1 |
| `start_date` | date | вң… Must-have | today | valid date | "2025-01-01" |
| `installments_paid` | int | вң… Must-have | 0 | 0 вүӨ x вүӨ total_installments | 3 |
| `total_amount` | decimal | Optional | auto-calc | computed: installment_amount Г— total_installments | 900.00 |
| `category` | enum | Optional | `other` | predefined list | "gadget" |
| `notes` | string | Optional | вҖ” | max 500 chars | "0% interest" |
| `color` | string | Optional | auto-assigned | hex color | "#4ECDC4" |

### 2.3 Shared Enums

**Categories:**
`entertainment` В· `food` В· `transport` В· `shopping` В· `gadget` В· `insurance` В· `education` В· `health` В· `utilities` В· `other`

**Billing cycles:**
`weekly` В· `biweekly` В· `monthly` В· `yearly`

### 2.4 Sensible Defaults

| Setting | Default |
|---------|---------|
| Currency | `MYR` (RM) |
| Timezone | `Asia/Kuala_Lumpur` (UTC+8) |
| Calendar start day | Monday |
| Billing cycle | Monthly |
| Start date | Today |

