### 3.2 Component Map (shadcn/ui)

| Component | Usage |
|-----------|-------|
| `Calendar` | Month view with custom day cells showing payment dots |
| `Sheet` (right drawer) | Day details drawer + create/edit item form |
| `Dialog` | Delete confirmation, upgrade prompt |
| `Card` | Upcoming items in sidebar, item summary cards |
| `Badge` | Category labels, status (paid/due/overdue), BNPL progress "3/6" |
| `Tabs` | "Subscription" / "BNPL" toggle in add/edit sheet |
| `Button` | Primary actions, mark-as-paid, quick-add FAB |
| `Input` | Text fields (name, amount, notes) |
| `Select` | Category picker, billing cycle, billing day |
| `DropdownMenu` | Item actions (edit, pause, delete), user menu |
| `Toast` (Sonner) | Success/error feedback ("Marked as paid вң“") |
| `Skeleton` | Loading states for calendar and sidebar |
| `Avatar` | User profile in header |
| `Separator` | Visual grouping in sidebar sections |
| `Progress` | BNPL installment progress bar |
| `Label` | Form field labels |
| `Switch` | Toggle active/inactive item |
| `Popover` | Quick month/year picker for calendar navigation |

### 3.3 Key Screens

#### Calendar Page (Main вҖ” `/dashboard`)
- **Month view** using shadcn `Calendar` with custom `DayContent` rendering:
  - Colored dots for each item due on that day
  - Dots: filled = paid, outlined = due, red = overdue
- **Month navigation**: `< February 2025 >` with `Popover` for quick jump
- **Summary bar**: "RM 580 due this month В· 3 items active"
- **Quick-add FAB**: Bottom-right floating `Button` вҶ’ opens `Sheet`

#### Upcoming Sidebar
- **Monthly total card** at top (glassmorphism/gradient card)
- **List of upcoming** items sorted by next due date
- Each item: icon/color dot В· name В· amount В· due date В· `Badge` status
- BNPL items show `Progress` bar (e.g., 3/6)

#### Day Details Drawer (`Sheet`)
- Opens when clicking a calendar day
- Shows all items due on that day
- Each item: name, amount, type badge, "Mark as Paid" `Button`
- Empty day: "Nothing due on this day рҹҺү"

#### Add/Edit Item Sheet (`Sheet`)
- `Tabs`: "Subscription" | "BNPL/Installment"
- Form fields per type (see section 2)
- Category `Select` with emoji indicators
- Color picker (6 preset colors)
- "Save" primary `Button` + "Cancel" secondary

#### Upgrade Dialog
- Triggered when user hits 3-item limit
- Shows: current count, Pro benefits, "RM10/month"
- "Upgrade Now" `Button` вҶ’ Polar embedded checkout

### 3.4 States

| State | Implementation |
|-------|---------------|
| **Empty** | Illustration + "Add your first subscription or installment" CTA (`Card` with dashed border) |
| **Loading** | `Skeleton` components for calendar grid + sidebar cards |
| **Error** | `Toast` (Sonner) with error message, retry option |
| **Limit reached** | `Dialog` with upgrade prompt when trying to add 4th free item |
| **No items on day** | "Nothing due today рҹҺү" in day drawer |

### 3.5 Accessibility Notes
- All interactive elements have `aria-label`
- Calendar navigation via keyboard (arrow keys)
- Color dots are paired with shapes (circle/diamond) for color-blind users
- Focus traps in `Sheet` and `Dialog`
- Toast announcements via `aria-live`
- Min touch target 44Г—44px on mobile
- Contrast ratio вүҘ 4.5:1 for all text

