## 8. Milestones

### Week 1: Foundation + Core CRUD

| Day | Task | Acceptance Criteria |
|-----|------|---------------------|
| **D1** | **Project setup** | Next.js configured, Tailwind + shadcn/ui initialized, Neon DB connected, Drizzle schema migrated, env vars set |
| **D1** | **Auth setup** | Better Auth configured with email/password + Google. Login/signup pages working. Middleware protects `/dashboard`. |
| **D2** | **Item CRUD** | Server actions for create/read/update/delete items. Free-tier limit (3 items) enforced server-side. |
| **D2** | **Item form UI** | Add/Edit item `Sheet` with `Tabs` (Subscription / BNPL). All fields working with validation. |
| **D3** | **Calendar view** | Month view rendering with payment dots on due dates. Month navigation working. Custom day cells with colored indicators. |
| **D3** | **Day drawer** | Click day вҶ’ `Sheet` opens with all items due. "Mark as Paid" button functional. |
| **D4** | **Upcoming sidebar** | Monthly total card. Sorted list of upcoming due items. BNPL progress bars. Responsive layout (desktop 2-col, mobile stacked). |
| **D5** | **Polish & empty states** | Empty state illustrations. Loading skeletons. Error toasts. Upgrade limit dialog (non-functional payment). |

### Week 2: Payments + Polish + Deploy

| Day | Task | Acceptance Criteria |
|-----|------|---------------------|
| **D6** | **Polar integration** | Polar product created. Checkout route working. Embedded checkout opens from upgrade dialog. |
| **D7** | **Webhook handler** | Webhook route receives events. Signature validation works. Entitlement updated on subscription create/update/revoke. Idempotency via `webhook_events` table. |
| **D7** | **Plan gating** | Pro users can add unlimited items. Free users blocked at 3 with upgrade prompt. Plan tier reflected in UI (badge in header/settings). |
| **D8** | **Settings page** | View account info. Manage subscription (link to Polar portal). See current plan. |
| **D8** | **Mark as paid logic** | Full flow: mark paid вҶ’ occurrence updated вҶ’ next_due_date recalculated вҶ’ BNPL completion auto-deactivates. |
| **D9** | **Responsive + a11y** | Mobile layout tested. Keyboard navigation. ARIA labels. Color-blind safe indicators. Touch targets. |
| **D10** | **Deploy + test** | Deploy to Vercel. Neon production DB. Polar production mode. End-to-end smoke test. Fix bugs. |

